title: r/Askreddit What Stranger Will You Never Forget? Do Aliens Love Dogs?
description: r/Askreddit In today's episode, users recount stories of strangers they will never forget, like a homeless guy who's been torn from his family and is desperate to perform a simple act of kindness, as well as a helpful stranger who returned a lost wallet without taking any of my money. You also get to hear my insane dog alien rant, which is even more ridiculous than it sounds. If you like this content, be sure to subscribe for more daily Reddit content!
